cs.DL, cs.IR, cs.DC, cs.CY, cs.CR 

The paper discusses the Open Archives Initiative (OAI) registration and validation services for data-providers, which are relevant to digital libraries (cs.DL), information retrieval (cs.IR), data curation (cs.DC), cybersecurity (cs.CY), and cryptography (cs.CR). However, since the paper focuses on the registration and validation services rather than the specific domain of the repositories, we cannot narrow down the sub-categories further.
